snippet.title: Floor Plan 2 - Launch Trailer (Oculus Quest | Rift & Steam VR)
snippet.description:
Put on your fanny pack and get in the elevator: Floor Plan 2 is now available on Oculus Quest, Rift, and Steam VR! 

Floor Plan 2 is a comedy adventure inspired by escape rooms, packed with more puzzles than you can fit in an elevator. For more information: www.elevator.how

Get it on Oculus Quest | Rift (Crossbuy): https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/2401648309868679/
Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1534850/Floor_Plan_2/

Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/turbobuttoninc/
